snippet.title: Tricky Typing Trailer
snippet.description:
Compete against your friends in this Absolutely Ridiculous Typing game! Using every single button on your controller (and then some), your typing skills will be put to the TEST as you type out each letter to compete in this Extravaganza 😈
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1453160/Tricky_Typing/
